<p>Running nvprof as follows <strong>works fine</strong>:</p>  <pre><code>$/path/to/cuda/6.5/bin/nvprof ./my_program </code></pre>  <p>Then I try to <strong>specify the output file</strong> with <code>-o</code>:</p>  <pre><code>$/path/to/cuda/6.5/bin/nvprof -o profile.nvprof ./my_program </code></pre>  <p>I get the following error (nothing more):</p>  <pre><code>======== Error: application not found. </code></pre>  <p>nvprof can find my application in the first case above, but it fails to find it when I also give an output file for the profile. <strong>What's wrong here?</strong></p>